- cs.RO (Robotics): The paper focuses on navigation tasks in real-world environments, which is a common problem in robotics. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision): The paper heavily relies on visual perception and recognition techniques, which are core topics in computer vision. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a deep reinforcement learning approach to learn navigation policies, which falls under the machine learning category. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper addresses a problem related to artificial intelligence, specifically in the area of autonomous navigation. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses the development of a control policy for navigation, which is a topic within systems and control.
